5
One Move Captures White (5)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0\deflang1033\deflangfe1042{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par \b Black to Play.\b0
\par Considering there is one space in which it is illegal for black to play, black has only four starting points to choose from.
\par
\par What is the best result?
\par Does it become a pae or can black captures white unconditionally?
\par }
