Diagram 1 (Pae)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par If this were a real game, nine out of ten players may have played dansu at 1.
\par
\par Is this pae the correct answer?
\par
\par No, it isn't. There is a move to capture white. This is as good as telling you where the correct answer is.
\par }
