Diagram 2 (Correct)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Black 1 is a lethal move. White is caught off guard.
\par
\par When dealing with life and death problems, an unexpected move often works so please read moves very carefully in real games.
\par }
